title: Dave Matthews Band ANTS MARCHING Promo Disc
description:
It is very rare Dave Matthews Band promo disc from 1995. It included studio and "radio edit" version of Ants (I don't have "radio edit" but it is the same version as studio but with shorten jam), and 2 live versions.

This CD was send to some radio stations in 1995 and it was not for sale. 

Orginal track list
1. Ants (radio edit)
2. Ants (studio)
3. Ants (live full band - 1995.01.30)
4. Ants (live dave matthews and tim reynolds - 1994.08.25)

MP3/320
